node.text: Today is a great day to start to taking steps to create change for Mother Earth. Please join @tentree and I in planting 50,000 trees. I know the words eco friendly or going green can be scary or hopeless but today we can make it easy...if you purchase the “Brie Bella Planting Package” on the tentree site you’ll be making an impactful change by planting trees. Head to my stories to understand how trees do more than being carbon neutral and head to the link in bio to join me on making this planet healthier. ✨
